Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的星核还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进 守护希望们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人去机场了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队被击败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去巴尔卡还是机场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空战队全部去机场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和陆战队去巴尔卡与守备队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光凭你们对抗阿撒谢尔型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是打不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出希望们 就撤退去机场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要和你并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向真壁发过誓要保护他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先去吧 我们也一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆路和水路都被占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃只能走空路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 艾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍后再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 等你来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你·在·那·里·吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会自己看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我是第二代戈班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在我方内部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断部队联络 招来Festum袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这是怎么做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望们之中可是有会读心之人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯利那加整个区都联络不上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种异常事态下竟然要人按兵不动？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对纳雷因见死不救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新国联总部的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的舰队请为发令做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发令？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利尼西亚轰炸基地有部队正在待命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部很可能发令执行针对对象全域的交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳雷因是人类军不可或缺的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情办完了吗 达斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我们也有可能要出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把机体准备好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们阿耳戈斯小队出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味着有哪个基地被攻下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人 还是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的工作纯粹是处理被敌人同化的人类 基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有可能扩大损失的人类 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一个人背负 也告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了搭救被同化的同伴而损失更多的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事绝不允许再度发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边明明更惨烈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要起飞吗 真是有勇气的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 支援他们脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上珀耳修斯中队之名 守护希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是第一迎击队 有人收到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们即将到达巴尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四守备队怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道森林区块陷落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 沃尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭救希望们是最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它…恶魔现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恶魔型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.86,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,663)}Diablo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死 宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被包围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些机体是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别代码还有效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会启动保险 无法攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人同化了森林区块的守备队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恶魔型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险还有效吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体上的芬里尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官机被夺取 无法访问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,删除机体识别代码
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战斗中的部队发令执行交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交战规定α 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认保险解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要误伤同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在攻击己方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…是被敌人同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人驾驶的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空路上无敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵入…内心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能脱离吗 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我开火 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我…消失之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 快开火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要取出驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不该来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死在这种…岛以外的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我…还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽要是再大点就能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老早就能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭 美羽已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是美羽早点把大哥哥们叫来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考联系？
