Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波信号 收到讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙宫岛部队 加入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 龙宫岛部队 加入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D岛的…Fafner？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是他们的城市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和预想的一样深入敌阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦到和平了吗 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好梦吧 应该
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体代码 Mk.Sein
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mk.Nicht…是总士学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了能令它们恐惧的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化敌人…吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑学长 果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说远见你们在找的东西可能会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会守护大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那或许就是我的生命仍在此处的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…我的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被同化的机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nicht可能会连下面的人类一起抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给你了 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半数已经不在了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命指征 0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半数幸存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已死亡的人也没有被同化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告司令所 被同化的机体都复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求解除交战规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复识别代码和保险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快疏导市民避难及重新构筑防线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个敌人会攻击驾驶舱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后？仅此而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化能力 我也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫洞的变形吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D岛的「存在」与「虚无」之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是救世主模型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:11.25,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(659,663)}Salvator
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲所追求的拯救人类之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除所有限制器驾驶的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无力守护…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害驾驶员 夺取机体的类型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨与虚无的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Nicht一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还没被机体吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群落就消灭到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去解决那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和追踪岛那只不一样的阿撒谢尔型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙要吞噬的是这城市的星核吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就必须守护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用手中力量的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何时候都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一己之命 生存之地 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人之尊严 安宁生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因这些面临剥夺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为守住这些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们使出所有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取着敌人的众多珍宝
